{"tid":2080670,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳也 #名采","createTime":"2020-06-26T14:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T14:54:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c4c555b88b92fa14d20f6b9c2aad7564c935e3","tid":2080670,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200626/20944184/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200626%2F20944184%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=3aa1f656\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200626%2F20944184%2F&h=73e0bea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200626/20944184/</a><br />\n<br />\n強忍淚水的八歲孩子 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200626/large/1593068770_004e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200626%2Flarge%2F1593068770_004e.jpg&h=75d6c872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八歲的孩子，法庭內聽到爸爸獲刑六周，雙眼通紅但強把淚水忍住。這位爸爸被控去年七一，在金鐘參與非法集結、「襲擊正當執行職務的警務人員X」。爸爸只承認集結，襲警罪則獲撤銷。案情重點一幕，是警方進行驅散時，爸爸跌倒，遭警制服被捕。跌倒又點襲警？睇另一樁案，被文宣海報貼落背脊都叫痛的阿蛇，就係告人襲警！社工劉家棟被控以身撞警盾，獲刑一年，令你想起雨傘運動中以胸襲警的女被告。胸襲新聞令香港一夜成名！<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強忍眼淚的八歲孩子，讓不行公義、不好憐憫的楊局長食住上抽水，威嚇小學老師，港版文革2.0㩒掣，學界跪玻璃比賽啟動，孤陋寡聞的香港人，淚眼中，真的見到了。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}